```json
{
"application": "FitHiChIP",
"other_software": [
"HiC-Pro",
"HiChIP-Peaks",
"bedtools"
],
"resource_requirements": {
"nodes": 1,
"processors": 1,
"memory": "100gb",
"walltime": "80:00:00"
},
"input_files": [
"validpairs file",
"peaks file",
"chromosome size file"
],
"output_files": [
"FitHiChIP-S10.loops.bedpe",
"FitHiChIP-S10.loops.bed",
"FitHiChIP-S10.filtered.loops.bedpe",
"FitHiChIP-S10.filtered.loops.bed"
],
"environment_variables": [
"PBS_O_WORKDIR",
"PBS_ARRAYID"
],
"script_purpose": "To call loops from HiChIP data using FitHiChIP",
"script_parameters": {
"peak_mode": "3",
"IntType": "3",
"BINSIZE": "10000",
"LowDistThr": "20000",
"UppDistThr": "2000000",
"UseP2PBackgrnd": "1",
"BiasType": "1",
"MergeInt": "1",
"QVALUE": "0.01",
"OverWrite": "1"
}
}
```
